SUMMARY:Summer Camp All Grown Up
DTSTAMP:20260619T041044Z
DTSTART:20260716T183000Z
DESCRIPTION:Why should kids have all the fun? Treat yourself to all the joy
	s of summer camp\, but for grown-ups! Unwind after a stressful day with ha
	nds-on nature activities\, crafts\, and outdoor exploration\, PLUS a simpl
	e snack and a refreshing beer from Saint Arnold Brewing Company. \n\n\n\nP
	lease dress for the weather and wear walking shoes. \n\n\n\n$22 member / $
	37 nonmember per classThursday\, June 18 and July 16Ages 21+ \n\n\n\n\n\n\
	n\nMicro World\n\n\n\nThursday\, June 18 \n\n\n\nThere’s a whole world of 
	activity going on under our noses. Using hand lenses and microscopes\, we’
	ll hunt for the tiny creatures that make our ecosystems function\, from ro
	ly-polies to plankton. We’ll even create a miniature world to take home: a
	 micro-terrarium! \n\n\n\n\nregister online\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCSI Nature\n\
	n\n\nThursday\, July 16 \n\n\n\nNature is full of mysteries\, and you can 
	find clues everywhere if you know what to look for. Learn about signs of w
	ildlife activity like tracks and scat\, make your own gourmet chocolate “s
	cat snacks\,” and search the trails for evidence of the Arboretum’s “usual
	 suspects.” \n\n\n\n\nregister online\n\nhttps://houstonarboretum.org/even
	t/summer-camp-all-grown-up/2026-07-16/\n\nFrom Houston Arboretum & Nature 
	Center
URL:https://houstonarboretum.org/event/summer-camp-all-grown-up/2026-07-16/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:houston-arboretum
CATEGORIES:Houston Arboretum & Nature Center
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
